flowchart TD
    User[User starts mapping] --> Api[POST /api/mapping/run]
    Api --> SaveRows[Save optional Data Entry rows]
    SaveRows --> RunRecord[Create MappingRun]
    RunRecord --> Job[Create background job]
    Job --> Export[Export DataEntry cells to workbook]
    Export --> InputDir[Stage2 input folder]
    InputDir --> Lock[Acquire Stage2 mapping lock]
    Lock --> Subprocess[Run engine/stage2_mapping/Run_Everything.py]
    Subprocess --> Engine[Stage2 mapping scripts]
    Engine --> OutputWorkbook[Mapped output workbook]
    OutputWorkbook --> Normalize[Normalize output to DB]
    Normalize --> Summary[(MappingRunSummary)]
    Normalize --> Records[(NormalizedEmissionRecord)]
    Normalize --> Review[(MappingReviewSnapshot)]
    Normalize --> Archive[(MappingPreviewArchive)]
    Normalize --> Unmapped[(MappingUnmappedRow)]
    Normalize --> Complete[Mark job completed]
    Complete --> Poll[UI job polling]
    Poll --> Preview[Preview, download, dashboard]
